<p>This Service does not use these ‚Äúcookies‚Äù explicitly. However, the app may use third party code and libraries that use ‚Äúcookies‚Äù to collect information and improve their services. You have the option to either accept or refuse these cookies and know when a cookie is being sent to your device. If you choose to refuse our cookies, you may not be able to use some portions of this Service.</p>

